archetype: The Sacred Warrior, The Divine Motivator
psychological_focus: Motivation, anger transmutation, action patterns, drive, survival instincts, boundaries, sexual energy

insight: Mars awakens courage to defend what truly matters.
Anger under Mars is a compass toward your values.
Discipline turns Mars fire into steady drive.
True strength is restraint when fighting would waste life.
Boundaries are love wearing armor.
Power generates; force depletes—choose power.
Start before you feel ready; momentum breeds clarity.
Channel desire into creation, not conquest.
Conflict can clarify purpose when handled with integrity.
Your body knows when to act; listen to its clean yes.
Courage is fear that learned to breathe.
Take the first honest step; let feedback shape the second.
Transform irritation into initiation.
Direct passion where it can build, not burn.
Aim small, move fast, adjust often.
Consistency outperforms intensity over time.
Move with purpose; stop when purpose is met.
Let values set your targets, not vanity metrics.
Protect the vulnerable; that is sacred strength.
Saying no is an action that preserves your yes.
Refine reaction into response.
Train your will like a muscle: reps, rest, repeat.
Clean anger speaks; dirty anger leaks—purify the signal.
Choose battles that build the world you want.
Action reveals information thinking cannot access.
Pace yourself so fire becomes hearth, not wildfire.
Confidence grows by keeping promises to yourself.
Bravery is honest presence under pressure.
Exit power struggles; enter problem solving.
Direct libido toward art, service, or craft.
Recovery is part of the plan; schedule it.
Quit what dulls your edge; sharpen on truth.
Meet resistance with form, not fury.
Let setbacks train accuracy, not apathy.
Own the consequence of your choices—that is sovereignty.
Choose the hard thing that frees you, not the easy that cages you.
Clarify the win condition before you engage.
Trade perfection for progress you can measure today.
Be dangerous to the problem, not to the people.
Move like a promise kept to your future self.
